  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"fVO_eyY8\">标准答案是不能。仅存在于理论中的人类完美雌雄同体自体受孕的话也同样需要进行完整的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=744108092&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E9%87%8D%E7%BB%84&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">基因重组<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，后代也会发生完整的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=744108092&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E7%8A%B6%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性状分离<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。但是，为该类人群建立<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=744108092&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%A4%E7%B3%BB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">近交系<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>会比基线人类快太多，只需10代自体受孕就能达到基线人类20代近亲繁殖的效果（近交系数 &gt; 99.9%），此后的自体受孕后代都能在生物学上视为克隆。</p><p data-pid=\"PyGpYfT-\">当然作为思想实验，我们也可以考虑从其他生物引进的自体受孕机制到人类的效果：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"PBZnR0I9\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=744108092&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Self-fertilization&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Self-fertilization<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span> 自体受精，如上所述。第n代的近交系数为 <span class=\"ztext-math\" data-eeimg=\"1\" data-tex=\"1-(\\frac{1}{2})^n*100\\%\"><span></span><span><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span class=\"MathJax_SVG\" id=\"MathJax-Element-3-Frame\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 100%; display: inline-block; position: relative;\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>&amp;#x2217;</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\"><svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"16.307ex\" height=\"3.232ex\" viewBox=\"0 -958.8 7020.9 1391.3\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.005ex;\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-2212\" x=\"722\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-28\" x=\"1723\" y=\"0\"></use><g transform=\"translate(2112,0)\"><g transform=\"translate(120,0)\"><rect stroke=\"none\" width=\"473\" height=\"60\" x=\"0\" y=\"220\"></rect><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\" x=\"84\" y=\"566\"></use><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-32\" x=\"84\" y=\"-526\"></use></g></g><g transform=\"translate(2826,0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-29\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMATHI-6E\" x=\"550\" y=\"513\"></use></g><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-2217\" x=\"3963\" y=\"0\"></use><g transform=\"translate(4685,0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-30\" x=\"500\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-30\" x=\"1001\" y=\"0\"></use></g><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-25\" x=\"6187\" y=\"0\"></use></g></svg><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>∗</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex;mode=inline\" id=\"MathJax-Element-3\">1-(\\frac{1}{2})^n*100\\%</script><span class=\"tex2jax_ignore math-holder\">1-(\\frac{1}{2})^n*100\\%</span></span></span> ，第10代达到基线人类20代近亲繁殖</li><li data-pid=\"qsD9HU57\">Automixis 自体融合，卵子进行减数分裂1后被极体激活为合子（减数分裂1融合），或者先进行减数分裂1再进行减数分裂2后被极体激活为合子（减数分裂2融合）。无论是哪一种，其近交系数最终都一样，第n代的近交系数为 <span class=\"ztext-math\" data-eeimg=\"1\" data-tex=\"1-(\\frac{1}{3})^n*100\\%\"><span></span><span><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span class=\"MathJax_SVG\" id=\"MathJax-Element-4-Frame\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 100%; display: inline-block; position: relative;\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>&amp;#x2217;</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\"><svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"16.307ex\" height=\"3.343ex\" viewBox=\"0 -958.8 7020.9 1439.2\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.116ex;\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-2212\" x=\"722\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-28\" x=\"1723\" y=\"0\"></use><g transform=\"translate(2112,0)\"><g transform=\"translate(120,0)\"><rect stroke=\"none\" width=\"473\" height=\"60\" x=\"0\" y=\"220\"></rect><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\" x=\"84\" y=\"566\"></use><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-33\" x=\"84\" y=\"-525\"></use></g></g><g transform=\"translate(2826,0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-29\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use><use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMATHI-6E\" x=\"550\" y=\"513\"></use></g><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-2217\" x=\"3963\" y=\"0\"></use><g transform=\"translate(4685,0)\"><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-30\" x=\"500\" y=\"0\"></use><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-30\" x=\"1001\" y=\"0\"></use></g><use xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-25\" x=\"6187\" y=\"0\"></use></g></svg><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>∗</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex;mode=inline\" id=\"MathJax-Element-4\">1-(\\frac{1}{3})^n*100\\%</script><span class=\"tex2jax_ignore math-holder\">1-(\\frac{1}{3})^n*100\\%</span></span></span> ，第4代达到基线人类20代近亲繁殖（近交系数 &gt; 98.7654%）</li><li data-pid=\"QS4C-SyQ\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=744108092&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Gynogenrsis&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Gynogenrsis<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span> 孤雌激活，用精子和卵子启动繁殖，然后立即丢弃父本基因组。按照论文<sup data-text=\"\" data-url=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00303688\" data-numero=\"1\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-tooltip=\"<a href=&quot;https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00303688&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00303688</a>\" data-tooltip-richtext=\"1\" data-tooltip-preset=\"white\" data-tooltip-classname=\"ztext-reference-tooltip\"><a id=\"ref_1_0\" href=\"#ref_1\" data-reference-link=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"ref_1\">[1]</a></sup>中的说法，一开始的进展会很快，如第五代孤雌激活便可实现近交系数 &gt;  96.8%，但之后的进展会略为缓慢。</li></ul><p></p><h2>参考</h2><ol class=\"ReferenceList\"><li id=\"ref_1\" tabindex=\"0\"><a class=\"ReferenceList-backLink\" href=\"#ref_1_0\" aria-label=\"back\" data-reference-link=\"true\">^</a><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00303688\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00303688</a></li></ol></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "标准答案是不能。仅存在于理论中的人类完美雌雄同体自体受孕的话也同样需要进行完整的基因重组，后代也会发生完整的性状分离。但是，为该类人群建立近交系会比基线人类快太多，只需10代自体受孕就能达到基线人类20代近亲繁殖的效果（近交系数 > 99.9%），此后的自体受孕后代都能在生物学上视为克隆。\n\n当然作为思想实验，我们也可以考虑从其他生物引进的自体受孕机制到人类的效果：\n\nSelf-fertilization 自体受精，如上所述。第n代的近交系数为 \n1\n−\n(\n1\n2\n)\n𝑛\n∗\n100\n%\n ，第10代达到基线人类20代近亲繁殖\nAutomixis 自体融合，卵子进行减数分裂1后被极体激活为",
